"best" is a relative term! also consider what TYPE of driving you are
going to be doing and the CONDITIONS.

the Yoko is a good tire for rain & pavement, but not for mud & snow. not
sure about the Michelin. check & see what its rated for.

also, go with the D load range for a Westy.

good luck,

